      <div1 id="BQ-15-2-0011">
        <head>
          <title type="section">
            <hi rend="b">NEWSLETTER</hi>
          </title>
        </head>
        <div2>
          <head>
            <title type="main">
              <hi rend="b">EXHIBITIONS : MORGAN LIBRARY</hi>
            </title>
          </head>
          <p>From 1 September through 4 October the Pierpont Morgan Library exhibited a selection of Blake
watercolors and illuminated books, including the Morgan (Butts) set of Job watercolors, watercolor designs to
<hi rend="i">L’Allegro</hi> and <hi rend="i">Il Penseroso</hi>, “Samson Breaking His Bonds,” “Fire,”
<hi rend="i">America</hi>, and the <hi rend="i">Songs.</hi> The Pickering Manuscript was also on exhibition,
along with engravings from books illustrated by Blake. A catalogue is available for $7.50.</p>
        </div2>
      </div1>
